headline: Eric Tsytsylin,  Rony Rothken
abstract: The couple met in December 2015 on The League, a dating app. After a few days of digital banter, they had their first date at a wine bar for which their dog is now named.
lead_paragraph: Eric Tsytsylin and Rony Rothken were married Jan. 11 at the Lighthouse at Chelsea Piers, an events space in Manhattan. Neil Timiraos, a friend of the couple who became a Universal Life minister for the event, officiated.
